# Root env reference for the docker-compose dev stack.
#
# The backend reads its own backend/.env (copy backend/.env.example → backend/.env
# and set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY). This file documents the few values compose itself
# cares about; service-to-service URLs are set in docker-compose.yml.
#
# Quick start:
#   cp backend/.env.example backend/.env   # then set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#   docker compose up --build
#
# Local sandbox WordPress (after `docker compose up`):
#   Site:  http://localhost:8080   (admin / admin)
#   API:   http://localhost:8000   (docs at /docs)
#   UI:    http://localhost:3000
